{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/44216", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/44216/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/44216/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/44216/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/44216", "id": 254343527, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyNTQzNDM1Mjc=", "number": 44216, "title": "Receiver::recv_timeout() returns instantly when duration overflows", "user": {"login": "vandenoever", "id": 608417, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjYwODQxNw==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/608417?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever", "html_url": "https://github.com/vandenoever", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vandenoever/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 211668062, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMTE2NjgwNjI=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-libs-api", "name": "T-libs-api", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the library API team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 6, "created_at": "2017-08-31T13:57:09Z", "updated_at": "2017-09-10T21:55:48Z", "closed_at": "2017-09-10T21:55:48Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "When Receiver::recv_timeout receives certain large values, it returns immediately. This is probably due to an overflowing value. Instead, when there is overflow, it should fall back to Receiver::recv.\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nuse std::sync::mpsc::Receiver;\r\nuse std::time::Duration;\r\n\r\nlet max = Duration::from_secs(u64::max_value());\r\nreceiver.recv_timeout(max);\r\n```\r\n\r\nInstant should probably not overflow like this:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nlet now = Instant::now();\r\nlet end_of_time = Instant::now() + Duration::from_secs(u64::max_value());\r\nprintln!(\"{:?}\", now);\r\nprintln!(\"{:?}\", end_of_time);\r\nprintln!(\"did we pass end of time? {}\", now > end_of_time);\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions":